description: The Euro STOXX 50 Short Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: 1x Short exposure to Eurozone blue chip companies listed in EUR in Eurozone countries Short exposure to 50 largest and most liquid companies Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review, largest component is capped at 10% Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.stoxx.com
name: Xtrackers Euro Stoxx 50 Short Daily Swap UCITS ETF 1C
